    "homepage": {
      "title": "Ship Smarter and Stay Competitive | PartnerShip",
      "description": "The relentless drive to be your shipping connection and help you ship smarter so you can stay competitive has been our goal since we were created.",
      "text_excerpt": "Ship Smarter and Stay Competitive | PartnerShip\nStay competitive.\nShip smarter.\nWith PartnerShip on your team, you can focus on running your business.\nLearn More »\nThere is no such thing as\nFree Shipping.\nWork with us and we'll help you ship smarter so you can stay competitive.\nLearn More »\nWe're here for your\n\"Oh Ship!\" moments.\nForget to ship something? Never shipped anything? Need more competitive costs? We'll help you ship smarter.\nLearn More »\nWe’re freight experts.\nLTL. Truckload.\nTime-Sensitive.\nWe get your load on the road so you can stay competitive.\nLearn More »\nRequest a Quote\nGet a competitive, no obligation freight quote with up-to-minute shipping rates from world-class carriers. If you already have a PartnerShip.com account, simply log in to get your custom rate.\nQuote Me »\nCreate an Account\nGet started now and create a PartnerShip.com account.  You’ll get access to our competitive freight rates and easy-to-use online shipping tools so you can quote, book, and track your freight.\nCreate My Account »\nShipping Analysis\nAre you spending more on your shipping than you have to? Let us provide you with a complete analysis to determine how you can save the most money on every shipment, from envelopes to full truckloads.\nAnalyze Shipping »\nWhy PartnerShip?\nFor Shippers\nPartnerShip helps you ship smarter by finding the best carrier, at the best price, to move your freight.  We can leverage our vast carrier network to secure competitive rates, providing you access to capacity at a moment’s notice.  With PartnerShip, you ship smarter, stay focused on your business, and maximize your productivity. That’s a powerful competitive advantage.\nShip with Us! »\nFor Carriers\nPartnerShip carriers enjoy access to profitable loads, fast payment and repeat business. We’ve provided shipping services to over 20,000 businesses across North America since 1989 by developing meaningful partnerships with our customers and our carriers. We work with the best national, regional, and local carriers, just like you, so become a PartnerShip carrier today.\nBecome a Carrier »\nPartnership Updates\nYour Essential Guide to the 2026 FedEx and UPS Rate Increases\n04/07/2026\nFedEx and UPS will be increasing their rates by an average of 5.9% in 2026. Learn what that means and what you can do to keep your costs under control.\nLearn More »\nHow to Calculate Freight Density for Shipping\n03/09/2026\nDensity is a major factor in determining your freight class and your total shipment cost. Learn how to calculate freight density in four easy steps.\nLearn More »\nLTL vs. Truckload Freight. What’s the Difference?\n02/22/2026\nUncover the key differences of LTL vs truckload freight and make smarter shipping choices. Explore the differences in transit time, handling, weight, shipment size, and pricing.\nLearn More »\nFor Good Measure: How to Avoid Freight Reweighs\n02/10/2026\nLTL shipping can be full of surprises, learn how to properly weigh your shipments so reweighs aren't one of them.\nLearn More "
    },
